        "content": "| Layer | Files | Key Risk |\n|---|---|---|\n| Crypto (HistoryOfThought) | 1 | Silent data loss, wrong-key decryption |\n| State (ExecutiveSpine) | 1 | Credit/health clamping bugs, timer leaks |\n| Events (EventBus) | 1 | Double-listener, dropped events unverified |\n| Routing (SovereignRouter) | 1 | Bad stream fallback corrupts session |\n| Text transforms (LiteralMode) | 1 | Regex order bugs, null crashes |\n| Services | 17 | All untested — scoring, reconciliation, AI prompts |\n| Components | 30+ | Full UI flows untested |\n\nStart with HistoryOfThought — it handles encryption of student work and is the highest-risk untested code in the repo.",
